property.name: note
property.value:
A slow track that evokes a mix of peace and wistfulness, a love for home, warmth, and safety. Good for kind traditions, homesickness, players weathering storms, being emotionally close to each other, or other such cases.
Very fun example of using Command Instruments. Also uses some weird quirks of how AHDSR works when stopping & releasing the event, which means this event will live a lot longer than expected after it's stopped.
